race.comment: JV LA TOXICA (1) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 229m at this track, beaten 0.6 lengths into sixth. Finds a nice race and can feature in the finish. BABES REVIVAL (10) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 201m at this track, beaten 3 lengths into sixth. Tackling a more suitable race this time so she is sure to be prominent. LETHAL EXECUTIVE (6) missed the placings two starts back then ran a better race and finished 1.75 lengths away in fifth last time out over 229m at Gillespie County Fairground. Has the ability to take this out. EYEAMCHAMPAGNEQUEEN (7) was in a rearwards position on the turn last time out before finishing 5.5 lengths back in ninth over 274m at Retama Park (Dirt). In the mix. Something for the Multiples: CANDELA RUNNER (4)
